[[File:Ruusancrystal.jpg|thumb|right|A Ruusan crystal.]]
'''Ruusan crystals''' came from the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of the [[Ruusan/Legends|same name]], were apreciated for their beauty and used like a form of currency in the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]]. While not directly affecting a [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber's]] effectiveness, they aided a [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] in focusing [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]. Ruusan crystals were lost after the [[Ruusan Reformations/Legends|Ruusan Reformation]].

